sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant A as ReAct Agent :8082
    participant L as LLM · Claude / Ollama
    participant M as MCP Server :8083
    participant DB as MongoDB

    U->>A: POST /api/agent/query
    A->>M: initialize + tools/list
    M-->>A: available tool schemas

    loop ReAct steps
        A->>L: Thought prompt
        L-->>A: Action + Action Input
        alt local tool
            A->>A: search_pdf / web_search
        else mcp tool
            A->>M: tools/call
            M->>DB: CRUD
            DB-->>M: result
            M-->>A: CallToolResult
        end
        A->>L: Observation
    end

    L-->>A: Final Answer
    A-->>U: JSON response
